[2026-03-15T16:16:54Z] [llm] {"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01WJ3dv2tt3U5N3cEvcAex23","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now I have all the information needed. Let me compile a comprehensive report of the findings.\n\n## Summary of Evolution Knowledge Base and Audit Logger Files\n\nI've completed a thorough review of all files related to the evolution knowledge base and audit logger. Here's what I found:\n\n### 1. **audit.go** - Full Contents\n**Location:** `/workspace/internal/evolution/audit.go` (113 lines)\n\nThe AuditLogger struct manages evolution artifacts:\n- **Log()** - Appends EvolutionResult entries as JSONL to `.cloche/evolution/log.jsonl`\n- **Snapshot()** - Creates timestamped copies of files in `.cloche/evolution/snapshots/` (format: `YYYYMMDDTHHMMSS-filename`)\n- **UpdateKnowledge()** - Appends lessons to knowledge base files at `.cloche/evolution/knowledge/<workflow>.md` in markdown format\n\n### 2. **Test Files for Audit.go**\n**Location:** `/workspace/internal/evolution/evolution_test.go` (lines 160-235)\n\nTests cover:\n- `TestAuditLoggerAppendsJSONL` - Verifies JSONL line appending\n- `TestAuditLoggerSnapshot` - Verifies file snapshotting with timestamps\n- `TestAuditLoggerUpdatesKnowledge` - Verifies markdown lesson appending with structured format\n\n### 3. **Config Structs with MaxPromptBullets**\n**Location:** `/workspace/internal/config/config.go` (lines 20-25)\n\n```go\ntype EvolutionConfig struct {\n    Enabled          bool   `toml:\"enabled\"`\n    DebounceSeconds  int    `toml:\"debounce_seconds\"`\n    MinConfidence    string `toml:\"min_confidence\"`\n    MaxPromptBullets int    `toml:\"max_prompt_bullets\"`\n}\n```\n\n**Default value:** 50 (line 48)\n**Tests:** `/workspace/internal/config/config_test.go` (lines 12-42)\n\n### 4. **Knowledge Base File Format**\n**Location:** `/workspace/.cloche/evolution/knowledge/develop.md`\n\nFormat for each lesson entry (JSONL+Markdown hybrid):\n```markdown\n- **[lesson-id]** (category, confidence: level) insight_text\n  _Action: suggested_action_\n  _Evidence: run-id-1, run-id-2, ..._\n```\n\nSupported categories:\n- `prompt_improvement` - Update existing prompt files\n- `new_step` - Add new workflow steps (type: script or agent)\n\nConfidence levels: `high`, `medium`, `low`\n\n### 5. **All Files in internal/evolution/**\n\n| File | Purpose | Lines |\n|------|---------|-------|\n| `audit.go` | JSONL logging, snapshots, knowledge base updates | 113 |\n| `types.go` | Core types: Lesson, EvolutionResult, Change, CollectedData | 56 |\n| `collector.go` | Gathers runs, prompts, knowledge base, workflow content | 91 |\n| `classifier.go` | LLM-based classification (bug/feature/feedback/etc) | 50 |\n| `reflector.go` | LLM-based lesson extraction from run history | 116 |\n| `curator.go` | Merges lessons into prompt files (ACE-style, strips code fences) | 130 |\n| `scriptgen.go` | LLM-based script generation for new validation steps | 72 |\n| `orchestrator.go` | Wires all stages, handles new step DSL mutations | 230 |\n| `trigger.go` | Debounced trigger (per project+workflow) | 63 |\n| `llmclient.go` | Command-based LLM invocation with -p, --system-prompt flags | 58 |\n| `evolution_test.go` | Comprehensive tests for all stages (948 lines) | 948 |\n| `trigger_test.go` | Tests for debounce behavior | 89 |\n\n### Key Implementation Details\n\n**Lesson Structure** (types.go):\n```go\ntype Lesson struct {\n    ID              string   `json:\"id\"`\n    Category        string   `json:\"category\"` // \"prompt_improvement\" or \"new_step\"\n    StepType        string   `json:\"step_type,omitempty\"` // \"script\" or \"agent\"\n    Target          string   `json:\"target,omitempty\"`     // path for prompt updates\n    Insight         string   `json:\"insight\"`\n    SuggestedAction string   `json:\"suggested_action\"`\n    Evidence        []string `json:\"evidence\"`\n    Confidence      string   `json:\"confidence\"`\n}\n```\n\n**EvolutionResult Structure** (types.go):\n- ID, ProjectDir, WorkflowName, TriggerRunID, Timestamp\n- Classification (from Classifier)\n- Changes (array of Change with Type, File, Reason, Snapshot)\n- KnowledgeDelta (summary of lessons applied)\n\n**File Paths:**\n- Knowledge bases: `.cloche/evolution/knowledge/<workflow>.md`\n- JSONL log: `.cloche/evolution/log.jsonl`\n- Snapshots: `.cloche/evolution/snapshots/<YYYYMMDDTHHMMSS>-<filename>`\n\n**Configuration Location:** `.cloche/config.toml` (per-project) or `~/.config/cloche/config` (global)\n\nAll paths are absolute and scoped by project directory."},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: aa5a2bce4defe4465 (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 63788\ntool_uses: 26\nduration_ms: 29902</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"016a7e3e-d9d2-46f5-8da9-2b20f96020ee","uuid":"7f6cdaf4-87e6-4262-a872-8ffbdcc12dea","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Find and read all files related to the evolution knowledge base and audit logger. I need:\n1. internal/evolution/audit.go - full contents\n2. Any test files for audit.go\n3. Any config structs that reference MaxPromptBullets\n4. The knowledge base file format (any .md or other knowledge files)\n5. Any other files in internal/evolution/\n\nBe very thorough - read all files completely.","agentId":"aa5a2bce4defe4465","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now I have all the information needed. Let me compile a comprehensive report of the findings.\n\n## Summary of Evolution Knowledge Base and Audit Logger Files\n\nI've completed a thorough review of all files related to the evolution knowledge base and audit logger. Here's what I found:\n\n### 1. **audit.go** - Full Contents\n**Location:** `/workspace/internal/evolution/audit.go` (113 lines)\n\nThe AuditLogger struct manages evolution artifacts:\n- **Log()** - Appends EvolutionResult entries as JSONL to `.cloche/evolution/log.jsonl`\n- **Snap